{"tid":2332952,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃秋生將「服」字退回蕭芳芳：把妳的愛情還給妳","createTime":"2020-12-20T04:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T06:28:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"10bc63c63a446f29c9b51e8e73064fe01dfd42ac","tid":2332952,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T04:45:40.000Z","msg":"黃秋生一直勇於發言，不平則鳴，今日凌晨他在社交網貼73歲影后蕭芳芳送給他的親筆提字「服」，原來當年蕭芳芳看了電影《無間道》後，十分佩服秋生的演技，寫了一個「服」字傳真給他，事隔多年，秋生在社交網貼出這個字，留言：「把妳的愛情還給妳。」及「保護兒童」，疑似不滿身為「護苗基金」創辦人的蕭芳芳，對最近一宗毒品調查科男警涉性侵6女童案件默不作聲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201220/GZUYNSQ36RAPBHDDOQHYDPCQJA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201220%2FGZUYNSQ36RAPBHDDOQHYDPCQJA%2F&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWEkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=629d41b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201220%2FGZUYNSQ36RAPBHDDOQHYDPCQJA%2F&h=92a30930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201220/GZUYNSQ36RAPBHDDOQHYDPCQJA/</a>"},{"pid":"3c66f2bc72660892c952489293c31472677b4a17","tid":2332952,"uid":290870,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T04:48:21.000Z","msg":"上次克警撞低小妹妹單野佢又係無出聲<br />\n不過算啦, 佢係林鄭個frd, 點會出聲?"},{"pid":"796e575c51c6080d82d3c897ece79ec8310af671","tid":2332952,"uid":179409,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:02:29.000Z","msg":"蕭芳芳呢類人欺世盜名<br />\n扮晒有愛心<br />\n實則只會嚮無風險、有光環嘅時候先會出聲<br />\n冒住得罪權貴風險替公義發聲？<br />\n你估個個係葉德嫻咁執言仗義咩"},{"pid":"688d1522b5d7624252187dae86d457032cfc2d6d","tid":2332952,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:29:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"06bc5f1769c10e57d1efe10e16f6c85423997f98","tid":2332952,"uid":37413,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:53:51.000Z","msg":"呢啲人只會譴責老遠對自己冇威脅講出嚟唔會比人鬧嘅人嚟譴責<br />\n兩個字概括呢亭人 - 偽善"},{"pid":"939cfd6af0c94dd67d